"   /gnu/store/nlma1pw0p603fpfiqy7kn4zm105r5dmw-util-linux-2.21.drv\n"
"@dots{}\n"
msgstr ""
"$ guix build emacs --dry-run\n"
"Les dérivations suivantes seraient construites :\n"
"   /gnu/store/yr7bnx8xwcayd6j95r2clmkdl1qh688w-emacs-24.3.drv\n"
