msgstr "{paramètre de @code{cups-configuration}} non-negative-integer max-jobs"

#. type: deftypevr
#: doc/guix.texi:17540
msgid "Specifies the maximum number of simultaneous jobs that are allowed.  Set to 0 to allow an unlimited number of jobs."
